task.summary: Default task
JSON and XML experiments
Bug fixes for ActiveConstituentFluxes and ActiveDerivedConstituentsCard. Added function to compute the output waterbody, and used this to fix a bug.
Moved all classes to new packages to be compatible with the WAT source tree.
Changed load function to not require an input filename. The fully qualified path to w2_con.npt is used instead.

Added support for expanding and shrinking the cards in W2ControlList to accommodate changes in the sizes of Cards. The updateTable method in all cards with more than one data line have been updated to first clear the table (data lines) and then add rather than set each line of data to the table.
Added test for expanding and shrinking cards.
Added constructor to Parser that creates the W2 control file object. Renamed all of the non-Card classes to W2____.java
Bug fixes, new Bonneville 5 yr transition model, new folders.
Added Spokane control file
Bug fixes, new data, new incomplete class to convert models using Excel date number to the legacy Julian day (day of year) format.
Implemented new W2Card in three classes and parser, and added some tests and documentation.
Updated GridCard
Updated TimestepControlCard and tests
Updated HeatExchangeCard and tests
Updated IceCoverCard and tests.
Updated InitialConditionsCard and tests
Renamed InOutflowCard to InflowOutflowCard and updated to use new W2Card class. Updated tests.
Updated LocationCard and tests
Updated MiscellCard and tests
Updated NumberStructuresCard, tests, and other misc. changes.
Updated RestartCard and tests. This is not currently used in W2Parser.java.
Updated SedimentCard, tests, and W2Parser
Added SnapshotPrintCard, updated SnapshotSegmentCard, added new tests, deleted old tests.
Updated TimeControlCard and tests.
Updated TsrPlotCard, tests, and W2Parser
Upudated WithdrawalOutputCard, tests, and W2Parser. Renamed W2Card_NEW to W2Card. Note: still need to update the multi-record and mult-line cards to use the new W2Card class.
Replaced MultiRecordRepeatingStringCard with separate cards, added tests, and implemented in W2Parser.
Minor bug fix in test.
Added classes. Completed ConvertExcelDateNumToJday class to convert W2 models from Excel date number to Julian day.
Updated ConvertExcelDateNumToJday and renamed fields in TimeControlCard.
Changed format to two decimal places in TimeControlCard.
Major updates to ConvertExcelDateNumToJday and tests. Added new test code to finish converting the W2 transition models from Excel date number to Julian day.
Minor updates
Corrected isOn function to return true if the value is ONH or ONS.
Updated W2Parameter to include a short location name compatible, as used in the original parser.exe program, and also a W2 parameter name such as is used in the CE-QUAL-W2 program and user's manual.
Adding new fields to W2Parameter and refactoring W2Parser. Not finished.
Finished adding new fields to W2Parameter and W2Parser.
